      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "どこか隠れる場所……隠れる場所……！\n{user}さん！　こっちへ！",
      "startTime": 22.4911567688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そっちは観葉植物しかないが\nまさかその後ろに隠れるのか！？",
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoentrance-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "それしかないです！　声を出さないでっ、息を潜めて！\nほら、腕を上げて下さい！　枝になりきって……！",
      "startTime": 36.2068257332,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 30.7401590665
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3859.840933500003,
          "startTime": 34.6
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5803.8121859,
          "startTime": 36.5439712524
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "無茶を言うな！　くっ、だがやるしかないか\nう、腕を枝のようにしならせて……",
      "startTime": 46.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_handcuffs-01.m4a",
